title: Cops Season 3 1990-1991
description:
Picked apart and pieced together by Tastypickles
Presented in per-season torrents with full air dates and episode descriptions.

Some episodes were misnumbered in their original torrents and have been corrected using the guide at http://thetvdb.com/?tab=seasonall&id=74709

The video and audio quality are all over the map - these are TV caps that in earlier seasons are over 20-25 years old! These are mostly not available on DVD.

Episodes have been spot checked for playability, and in some cases a partially damaged episode may exist simply because most of it will play.
